title: Fantasy Book v5#2 (#20) 1986-06
description:
Fantasy Book Vol. 5 No. 2 (whole issue 20), June 1986.

This magazine is a fantasy and science fiction anthology (ISSN 0277-0717) edited by Dennis Mallonee, Nick Smith, Forrest J. Ackerman, Jessica Salmonson, and Darrell Schweitzer which I have reproduced here as an OCR'd PDF. Contents:

Davidov, Harry: The Wizard of the Wood
Dorr, James S.: A Neo-Canterbury Tale
Farnham, Lynn: The Apprentice
Friesner, Esther M.: Taverna
Goldin, Stephen: The Castle at the Top of the World, Part I
Hughes, Kim: The Soulsongs of New Caledonia
Hussey, Leigh Ann: Sword-Kin
Lee, Rebecca: Walking the Beat on the Outskirts of Hell
Swigart, Rob: In the Net of Life and Time
Thompson, Kristine K.: And His Fingers Were Ever Straying...
Zimmer, Paul Edwin: A Swordsman from Carcosa, Part II
